---
title: Italian-Spiced Double Salmon with Tuscan-Inspired Salad
description: Ciao Bella! Italian-spiced salmon is the star tonight but chewy ciabatta, crisp arugula and salty capers come together to create a refreshing salad that completes this ideal weeknight meal. Pour the wine and set the table!
